    schema1:description "Clive joined HMT in May 2022 as Head of the Government Risk Profession. Clive was at EY for 17 years (the last 9 of which were as a Partner) where among other responsibilities he led the development of client-facing risk management practices, ran a digital learning & communication business, and had overall responsibility for everything the firm did for some major financial services clients in London, New York and Zurich."@en ;
